set-bg: img/fondo_escritorio.jpg
new-page: true

> *"No queremos olimpiadas, queremos revolución."*

 - pinta estudiantil, Ciudad de México, 1968

> *"¿Quién? ¿Quiénes? Nadie. Al día siguiente, nadie."*

 - Rosario Castellanos, *Memorial de Tlatelolco*

This is a game of history and counter-history. You will lead the Mexican left from the smoke of Tlatelolco toward an election twenty years away, through a state that prefers buying its enemies to burying them, but keeps both instruments oiled. Historical accuracy is taken seriously; where you bend history, the game will bend with you.

The dead in this game were real. They are treated accordingly.

